                Aelia Nice <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">vi</supplied>x</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> annis XC <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Victor vi<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>x</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> a</supplied>nnis IIII Aelia Mam<lb break="no" n="3"/>mutio <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> annis XXII <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Vitalia<lb break="no" n="4"/>nus augur <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>NMOO matri et <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>neptiae <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erentibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Daicoviciu: abweichende Textwiedergabe; ILD: Z. 5: neptae; Gudea - Lucăcel: geringfügig abweichende Textwiedergabe. Die Tafel ist in vier Teile zerbrochen.</p>
            </div>
